name: L.N. Fabtech
overview:
Established at Karnataka, India in 2012, we L.N. Fabtech are leading names in the industry, engaged in manufacturing, supplying and providing services for wide array of Hand Pallet Trucks, Battery Operated Pallet Trucks, Hand Operated Stackers, Battery Operated Stackers, Roller Conveyors and many others.

Products & Services: Industrial Stackers Scissor Lifts Goods Lifts Floor Cranes Industrial Cranes Industrial Conveyors Maintenance Services

Infrastructure: We are supported by technically advanced manufacturing facility that is outfitted with advanced technologies and facilities. All the departments are well-segregated into different sections that assist us to smoothly facilitate the entire business operations.

Quality: Quality is considered as the prime concern of our organization, and in order to maintain the same we fabricate our entire product range using quality assured raw components and sophisticated technologies. Our entire product array is in compliance as per the set quality standards and guidelines.

Our Team: We are supported by the panel of experienced and prolific professionals, who assists us in achieving the desired organizational goals and maintain the healthy and cordial relationships with our clients.

Why Us?: Being client-centric firm, our prime concern is to cater diverse requirements of the clients within limited time frame. We offer easy payment modes and maintain cordial terms to maintain long term relationships. We follow transparent business strategies in our entire business operations.
